title: Graylog: Nodes
agents: graylog
catalog: app/graylog
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 With this check you can monitor graylog nodes. It outputs the load balancer,
 lifecycle and processing state. Also the number of inputs is shown. The
 long_output gives detailed information about the inputs of the node.

 Needs the datasource "Check state of Graylog" to be configured.

item:
 The item is the name of the node.

inventory:
 One service for each node {"Graylog Node my_node"} will be created.
